<TEXT>
President Reagan relaxed at his 
mountaintop ranch Monday enjoying a second straight day of sunny 
clear weather 
The president who arrived here Saturday evening had breakfast 
with his wife Nancy and then the two of them went horseback 
riding 
He planned to spend the day doing ranch chores and reviewing 
paperwork according to a White House statement 
Reagan will return to Washington on Wednesday the day before 
his administration submits its new budget to Congress 
